Now you can ask AI questions and chat with AI  directly in Google. 
For the first time Ask AI and Ask the Community are combined in one easy to use widget.
We use AI from ChatGPT , Open AI, Wikipedia and other AI solutions in one to give you a customized search and chat experience.
As a featured  Search Tool over five years we have made enhancements to our Search and Chat Features that include AI , real time chat, Ask the Community and more. 
  Some of the new features 
* Talk directly to AI right from Google 
* Talk directly to the community on any website 
* Right click on any text anywhere to " Ask AI" while reading an article
